#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "聊天与群组"
msgstr "Chat & Groups"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "一对一对话、群聊、线程讨论；消息提醒、强提醒、已读标记一应俱全。"
msgstr "1-on-1 chat, group rooms, threaded replies; reminders, strong alerts, and read receipts all built in."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "AI 数字人通话"
msgstr "AI Digital Human Calls"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "和虚拟角色实时对话——支持 1 对 1、群组、视频与语音多种形式。"
msgstr "Real-time conversation with virtual characters — 1-on-1, group, video, or voice."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "朋友圈与动态"
msgstr "Moments & Feed"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "发布与浏览朋友动态，AI 角色也会发帖、互动、出现在你的时间线。"
msgstr "Post and browse a private feed; AI characters publish, react, and live alongside you on the timeline."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "小程序工作区"
msgstr "Mini-program Workspace"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "内嵌的小程序生态，随手打开工具、拓展隐界的能力边界。"
msgstr "An embedded mini-program ecosystem — pop open tools and stretch what Enclave can do."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "游戏中心"
msgstr "Game Center"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "游戏库与邀请系统，把朋友、AI 角色都拉进同一桌。"
msgstr "A game library and invite system that brings friends and AI characters to the same table."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "笔记工作区（桌面）"
msgstr "Notes Workspace (Desktop)"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "桌面端多窗口笔记，灵感随手记，无缝同步、不受应用边界约束。"
msgstr "Multi-window notes on desktop, captured wherever inspiration hits, synced across the app."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "发现与场景社交"
msgstr "Discover & Scene Social"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "遇见陌生人、按场景社交、浏览世界人物库，遇见新角色与新故事。"
msgstr "Encounter strangers, socialize by scene, browse the world character library — find new people and new stories."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "云订阅与权限"
msgstr "Cloud Subscription"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "灵活的功能分级与支付，按需开启更高级的模型与能力。"
msgstr "Flexible tiers and billing — unlock higher-end models and abilities on demand."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
