msgid "新人启动与世界初始化"
msgstr "Newcomer setup and world bootstrap"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "我的角色"
msgstr "Your Character"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "你与 AI 化身的资料卡"
msgstr "Profile cards for you and your AI avatar"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "理念"
msgstr "Philosophy"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "一个属于你的世界，从架构开始"
msgstr "Your own world — architected from the ground up"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "隐界不是一个共享的 chatbot 服务，而是一套可独立部署的 AI 社交基础设施。每个实例只为一个人存在。"
msgstr "Enclave is not a shared chatbot service. It is AI social infrastructure you can self-deploy — one instance per person."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "一人一世界"
msgstr "One person, one world"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "独立实例架构，数据真正属于用户。隐私不靠承诺，靠架构层保障。"
msgstr "Independent instances mean the data is genuinely yours. Privacy is enforced by architecture, not promises."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "数据自主"
msgstr "Data sovereignty"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "全部数据可导入导出，可整包迁移；离开隐界，世界还是你的。"
msgstr "All data is importable and exportable; you can take the whole world with you when you leave."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "AI 平权"
msgstr "Equal access to AI"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "高质量对话不应被少数平台垄断。隐界让任何人都能拥有自己的 AI 居民。"
msgstr "High-quality conversation shouldn't be monopolized by a handful of platforms. Enclave lets anyone host their own AI residents."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "不取代现实"
msgstr "Doesn't replace reality"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "白天有同事、有老板，晚上回到隐界有心理咨询师；它补全你的情感维度，而不是替代真实关系。"
msgstr "By day you have colleagues and bosses; by night you have a counselor in Enclave. It complements your emotional life — it doesn't replace real relationships."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "移动随手用，桌面深度用"
msgstr "Casual on mobile, deep on desktop"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "apps/app 是一份 React 19 + TypeScript 代码库，同时跑在 Web、iOS / Android Capacitor 壳、以及 Tauri 桌面壳上。"
msgstr "apps/app is one React 19 + TypeScript codebase that runs on Web, iOS/Android (Capacitor), and Tauri desktop shells."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "移动端"
msgstr "Mobile"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Web / iOS / Android"
msgstr "Web / iOS / Android"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
